Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:02:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔、柚姬谈论
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常像ちぃ的電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不太像是恶作剧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后还有其他\N与寄图者有关的线索吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，暂时还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬你不需要道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再确认一次看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.93,0:02:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能调出收到这张图当天的资料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许会发现些什么也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片怎麼看都像是ちぃ對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽…虽然不知道是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過看起來很像ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且这堆乱七八糟的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也没看过这种接头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是恶作剧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在某處看過ちぃ的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先拍下她的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后合成出这张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过总觉得其中并不单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被手郲住的这个字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是“ C ”的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C、H、O、B、I、T …
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之前应该跟你说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以“ Chobits ”为代号的\N那台传说中的电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拥有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能够自己思考行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拥有人的外表
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却又不是人的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我问你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片是ちぃ嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那果然是恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本没必要操这个心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，ちぃ她…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ就是ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ自己也不記得這張圖片…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实根本谈不上什么记忆\N因为资料跟OS都不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能否让我插句话呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重新查詢看看\Nちぃ至今做過的事如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許會發現\Nちぃ與圖片的關連性也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和，你问她一下电话号码
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先别管那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你知道我的电话号码吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.27,0:05:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,03-68828-52DF3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说话了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次講出“ちぃ”以外的字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她有安装学习软件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是被丢在垃圾堆里，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是在被丢掉前初始化了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.85,0:05:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是这样\N但学习机能却还留着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果好好教她\N我想她不但能够说话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也能够做其他事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你好好教她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为她现在的主人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她会按 照你教她的方式行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了？ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽会时的暗号遭到利用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惨遭妻子杀害的女人怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今仍徘徊在那间公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在跟她遇害当天\N同样的闷热阴天里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就会发出那个暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人以前所用的幽会暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将房间的电灯关了又开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关了又开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后在那里等待着新的牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在G公寓的104号房里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那间不应该有的104号房
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个鬼故事\N说的果然就是 GAB 城崎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去 GAB 城崎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去上面看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有…有人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身…身体动不了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，不能過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快动，快动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…ちぃ她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仓库？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为最近东西容易发霉潮湿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本想来个大扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是电灯泡快要坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直没办法打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了换灯泡\N我找来了各种东西垫脚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我还是碰不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会叫我来帮忙换
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是从门下面\N流出的黑色液体…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我搬桌子的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不小心打翻了水桶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候我有上去找本须和帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过你看起来好像很忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:09:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电灯泡、桌子、水桶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过为什么会有104号房？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来一楼本来有四间房间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁是103号房
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我搬来时做了一点改装
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缺的是102号房
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然被搞得团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经不害怕了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.27,0:09:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大魔王终于登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是打不倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他那么强吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.44,0:10:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看杂志和网路上的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没看过有人打倒过他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警告，警告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通过这里就可以到下个城镇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你是认真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别想不开了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是打不赢那家伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她也許正在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿他没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丝茉茉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,carbonara
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,chorizo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.83,0:11:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ち…ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時ちぃ明明沒有經驗值
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却打倒了游戏里的大魔王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:11:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和也不可能会写这种程式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道她真的不是普通的电脑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.79,0:12:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那个你有看到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树看到海豚的“哗啦”\N会很高兴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ也要來嘩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是不会游泳吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ち…ちぃ呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从表面看来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像也没进水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树，你在生气吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ做錯事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会生气呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真是台不可思议的电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般如果掉到海里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会进水，然后会很难修复
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ的相關記憶資料到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光靠我们果然还是\N有点资料不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找新保帮忙看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过新保少爷他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保，新保
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天先出门了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好严重的黑眼圈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熬夜了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像也很困的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清…清水老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我住一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然叫那么大声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.57,0:16:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要开始上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老师还没来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有时会早到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她从来没迟到过的说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有电话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我接通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:16:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个声音，你是新保对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在在搞什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟老师私奔…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们吵架了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们很久没有吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者应该说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连话都说不上两句
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上了门链就表示
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老公忘了我会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在不在家都没影响了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一想到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就觉得怎样都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得怎样都…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明在说这么伤心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她却没有哭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她其实很想哭出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是拼命在忍耐罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想至少让她在遇到\N不愉快或伤心的事时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能够哭个痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我迷上她了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此，为什么要私奔？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道只剩这个方法了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.59,0:19:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们这个年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是小鬼而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后你打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许就如同你所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过这是我的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决定？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变得不相信男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她认为就算一开始说喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦出现像电脑那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以迎合自己的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会完全改变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像从没喜欢过一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让她跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决定私奔到深山的温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个好地方喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样湿答答的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不过是旅行而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.03,0:19:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩恩爱爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说，这算是私奔啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在多香子点头之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不打算回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:19:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,点头？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我再婚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚，再婚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丝茉茉再帮我保管一段时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮你保管当然没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.22,0:20:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜罗，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会再跟你联络的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.62,0:20:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再有什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告诉我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像我这种重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮不了你太大的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过或许我可以帮上什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.24,0:20:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告诉我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.41,0:20:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.81,0:20:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像电脑那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以迎合自己的对象啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的，让我帮您泡杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是休息一下比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.51,0:21:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我这并不是累
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我當時分析ちぃ沒失敗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.23,0:21:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经做得很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.74,0:21:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假使这孩子学会了说话\N学会了做各种不同的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纵使她再怎么乖巧\N再怎么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劝你还是别喜欢上她比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:21:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不想在日后\N伤心流泪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,0:22:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.53,0:22:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,口味…不对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是用跟姊姊同样的方法泡的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好喝

